latestIgtvVideos.title: Prepare your skin Before Makeup with me🌸
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hi Guys!

Starting off with @perennecosmetics Makeup disinfectent To disinfect my all products .

THIS IS MY OWN VOICE VIDEO EXPLAING EACH AND EVERYTHING PROPERLY.

Hairband :- @beutifulbyssk 

Today I’m gonna share you my skin prepping before makeup!
So let’s know about the products 🌸:

1. Wiping off my face with A wet Tissue softly and gently.🌸

2.  After that, Taking @neutrogena  Hydroboost watergel to hyderate and moisturize my skin .
( I loved this product alot, Best suitable for Oily skin or acne prone skin)🌸

3. Now, Using @wowskinscienceindia  Vitamin C skin Mist toner , Which helps to absorb deep into the skin and gives a dewy, Radiant and soft skin.🌸

4.  After using a toner , Using @milagro.beauty  @royalicious1  Milagro Hydrogel . It’s mattifying gel sunscreen which is enriched with lots of essential oils and extracts. One of the most fine and non greasy product.🌸

5. For Moisturizing my Lips I’ve used @mynykaa  Lip Balm.🌸

6. To Make my lips more supple and soft and hyderated I’ve used @indulgeo.essentials  Lip pout. 🌸
 And finally, Spraying @iconic.london  Prep set and glow Mist on face to make my skin look glowly before Makeup.

So yeah , That’s how I prepare my skin before doing any kind of makeup. 
Preparing tpur skin before makeup is very important as it makes certain layers on your skin which protects your pores getting clogged , so that makeup could also look long lasting if the prepping is done properly.

I hope you guys must have liked my video . Do leave your valueable feedbacks kn the comment section.🥰

I’ll be coming with lots of new videos very soon! Takecare!!!❤️
.
.
